name: FifthGradeMathsTest
0:
”Alexa, open maths test”
”Alexa, play maths test”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: maths test
des: This skill starts a session of 15 questions, asked one by one. Questions will have three options (1 or 2 or 3) out of which you will have to select only one option. Result to the question will be given immediately (correct or incorrect). After asking 15 questions, you will be given your score. You will also have the option of reviewing the incorrectly answered questions. You get a chance to enter yourself in the leader board by answering all 15 questions correctly. Good luck!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
